Package: CRM2s
Type: Package
Title: C-Optimality Based Two-Stage Continual Reassessment Method (CRM)
Version: 0.1.0
Description: Implements CRM2s, a Two‑Stage Continual Reassesment Method based in c‑optimality. Simulates and compares this dose‑escalation method in phase I clinical trials with the traditional 3+3 design for two types of dose‑toxicity models: power with one parameter and logistic with two parameters.
URL: https://github.com/alvarocia/CRM2s
